 - undo/redo (provided)
 - cut/copy/paste (provided)
 - display of line numbers (provided)

Basic editing functions:
 - recent files (done)
 - goto line (done)
 - search (done)
 - replace (done)

Refactoring 
 - move global app data (recent files list, ...) to Bride object
 - new mechanism for menu initialization
 - enabling/disabling of menu commands if documents are opened or not

